    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is being sold strictly as-is. While the engine currently starts, it exhibits significant fluid leaks, a heavy knock, and persistent overheating issues that require immediate attention. The transmission is slipping badly, and the braking system needs a complete overhaul. Cosmetically, the body shows extensive rust, major dents, and failing paint, while the interior has significant tearing and several non-functional electronic components. This car is best suited as a dedicated project for a skilled mechanic or as a source for salvageable parts.",
