    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an automotive masterpiece in truly pristine condition. This vehicle represents the pinnacle of its class, having been maintained to exacting standards that far exceed typical ownership. From the flawless exterior finish to the untouched interior upholstery, every detail reflects a life of climate-controlled storage and meticulous care. This is an investment-grade example for the discerning driver who demands nothing less than showroom perfection. Experience the confidence of driving a vehicle that looks, feels, and performs as if it just rolled off the assembly line.",
