    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Step into a time capsule of pure, unadulterated passion. This isn't just a vehicle; it\u2019s a symphony of steel and leather, a masterpiece preserved for the discerning soul. Imagine carving through the mist of a coastal morning, the engine humming a deep, resonant baritone that vibrates through your very core. Every curve of its silhouette tells a story of elegance and speed, gleaming under the streetlights like a polished jewel. This car doesn't just transport you; it transforms every journey into a cinematic escape. It is a rare relic of an era where craftsmanship was king, waiting for its next curator to write the next chapter of its legendary life.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
